name: Fabric Bouquet
description:
These bouquets are made to last. Different color fabrics and embellishments to match your special day... contact us for a quote :) 

Each flower is handmade and assembled just for you. 

The bouquets even smell lovely!

Pricing varies on size and materials. 

*Please contact us for pricing and customization. All pieces are custom made to order, meaning the feathers and petals may vary slightly. Stones may vary depending on stock. As always, it will be made beautifully and with care!

name: End'it Bag
description:
Join us and the End It movement in ending modern day slavery by purchasing this bag. 

This 10 oz. 100% cotton canvas tote sheds light on the issue of human trafficking and modern day slavery taking place right now all over the world. Together, we can put an end to this injustice. Be a voice for the 27 million whose voice isn't heard. Make a global impact through your purchase! 

Proceeds go toward the Ragga'End It movement. 


*size is perfect for most laptops and books.
